Title: Commending the Future Farmers of America from Vernon, Verona and Sherrill, New York, on hosting 2020 Maple Weekends
ActClause: LEGISLATIVE RESOLUTION commending the Future Farmers of America (FFA) from Vernon, Verona, and Sherrill, New York, upon the occasion of hosting this year's Maple Weekends on March 21-22, 2020 and March 28-29, 2020
